SLIMEBOSS-NIBBLE_AND_LICK.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
Gain a [gold]Lick[/gold].{IfUpgraded:show:
Draw a card.|}

SLIMEBOSS-OVEREXERT.description:
Gain {PotencyPower:diff()} [gold]Potency[/gold].{IfUpgraded:show:
[gold]Command[/gold] twice.|}
In {OverexertPower:diff()} turns from now, [gold]Absorb[/gold] all Slimes.

SLIMEBOSS-SERVE_PROTECT.description:
Gain {CalculationExtra:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold] and {BlurExtra:diff()} [gold]Blur[/gold] for each Slime.
